item.title: Since it's free time, the front-end engineer tried Python (v3.7.5) for the first time.
item.description: #Greeting Hello. My name is Steve.T and I am a front-end engineer. I usually do Vue.js, React, and Angular. I wrote Python because I wanted to study something because it was completely full remote and I was free. Backend knowledge is stopped in PHP, I can not write Ruby or Python, it was a little … and I heard that Python is standard equipment for information processing tests, so I have to do this finally.
